  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study to determine whether high dose vitamin D has positive effect on
      behavior of autistic children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Double blinded placebo controlled study to determine effect of two different doses of vitamin
      D on Behavioral domains in autistic children.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
